{"tid":1826024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[捷報] 14歲小將於冰球項目奪金牌　實現香港冬季奧運零的突破","createTime":"2020-01-15T21:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T23:30:12.000Z","uid":18692,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6b4818a9ecb4cc73c5cba5ebe6ce3701095060","tid":1826024,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hX6uULH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhX6uULH.jpg&h=5031c8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於瑞士洛桑舉行的「第3屆冬季青年奧運會」3人冰球混合隊際賽決賽及銅牌戰上演，以14歲成為香港歷史上最年輕奧運選手的任遊，效力的綠隊擊敗紅隊奪金，另一香港選手徐綽希效力的啡隊則於銅牌戰險勝黑隊。首次派選手參賽的香港代表團就奪得1金1銅，寫下歷史新一頁。<br />\n<br />\n經過全球選拔，超過100名來自全球不同地區的球員混合組成8隊。任遊與意大利、挪威等代表組隊，為隊內惟一亞洲球員。他效力的綠隊於分組賽取得7勝1負，17分高踞榜首。徐綽希的啡隊以5勝2負排第二晉級4強。綠隊於4強順利以擊敗黑隊坐銀望金，而啡隊則落敗只能爭銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n決賽全場爆滿，超過一萬名球迷觀戰，綠隊決賽對陣紅隊，前者在首節已經強勢出擊連入三球，雖然在尾段紅隊追回兩球，惟首節綠隊仍以3：2領先。不過綠隊並未有給予對方追平的機會，在第二節以一段4：1的攻勢，一口氣拉開至4分進入最後一節，綠隊未有放軟手腳再攻入3球，最終以10：4大勝，奪得金牌。<br />\n<br />\n至於銅牌戰的戰況則相當緊湊，徐綽希效力的啡隊在最後關頭啡隊攻入一球，以6：5險勝黑隊，摘下一面銅牌。<br />\n<br />\n香港代表團自2002年派隊前往美國的鹽湖城參加冬季奧運會，前4次均為短道速滑選手，前年平昌冬奧則有吳一里首次參加高山滑雪。 <br />\n<br />\n團長霍啟剛於上月舉行的授旗禮表示，望藉參賽奧運增加外界對冬季運動項目的關注，發展設施配合香港運動員訓練。"},{"pid":"bc83f445afdfdfd0abfcaba62d3ed022dad81c40","tid":1826024,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xM7xSpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxM7xSpz.jpg&h=cd69f785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧運官網有任游訪問 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lausanne2020.sport/en/news/athletes/ice_hockey_players_talk_up_3_on_3_after_fantastic_tournament\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lausanne2020.sport%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fathletes%2Fice_hockey_players_talk_up_3_on_3_after_fantastic_tournament&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=d3e0237f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lausanne2020.sport/en/news/athletes/ice_hockey_players_talk_up_3_on_3_after_fantastic_tournament</a>"},{"pid":"7890778fa47586a877055c6dc291c6cb607dce09","tid":1826024,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:32:24.000Z","msg":"9成有錢仔"},{"pid":"dc9197805197930a9bf00c2220ac6ff63a443bb3","tid":1826024,"uid":134012,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7890778fa47586a877055c6dc291c6cb607dce09","tid":1826024,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:32:24.000Z","msg":"9成有錢仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:42:11.000Z","msg":"任遊三歲已與冰球結緣，全因他來自一個冰球世家：「我一開始係跟住阿哥（任懿）打冰球，佢就同我舅父打波；而舅父又係好細個已經開始打冰球。」<br />\n係100%"},{"pid":"4bcb02114d331899c258710aa9d001ef089b3e6d","tid":1826024,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac90dfbbd938ffb98effe85932bc4183f37a4e6","tid":1826024,"uid":304934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T22:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f041609391fc1965a47597c3263f8fd656690f8","tid":1826024,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7890778fa47586a877055c6dc291c6cb607dce09","tid":1826024,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T21:32:24.000Z","msg":"9成有錢仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:30:12.000Z","msg":"比你有錢都未必做到啦<br />\n成日睇人有無錢做乜9"}]}